data.description: Accepted Offer with Contingencies. Make your home dreams come true!  Tucked back @ a dead end street for privacy.   Home offers new carpet & paint inside as well as a newer heat pump and H2O heater.  Kitchen is large & offers an island for ease of gatherings. Great floor plan, w/ spacious rooms, inside utility, large primary bedroom w/ garden tub & shower.  2 additional bedrooms on the other end of home.  Bonus parking space w/ this lot, fenced yard & great storage.  Work shop in garage & shed outside.  Handicap ramp to access front door.
